  <titles>
    <title as="introduced" type="short">Amyotrophic Lateral Sclerosis (ALS) Research, Treatment, and Assistance Act of 1997</title>
    <title as="introduced" type="official">To amend the Social Security Act to waive the 24 month waiting period for Medicare coverage of individuals disabled with amyotrophic lateral sclerosis (ALS), to provide Medicare coverage of drugs used for treatment of ALS, and to amend the Public Health Service Act to increase Federal funding for research on ALS.</title>
